title: Cringeworthy Or Charming?
description:
Clinton Yates, Israel Gutierrez and Bill Barnwell debate if the the T-Wolves’ celebration was cringeworthy or charming and if they are convinced that the Nets can sustain their level of play from last night against the Celtics.
